With my recent small redesign and fancy printing (spot UV gloss!) I've had my #WalletDungeons generator bouncing around in my brain.

I'm already working on a derelict ship generator for my sci fi #cairn hack, but what other genres or locations would be fun for a different version of Wallet Dungeons?

Could be a simple reskin, or tweaking the generation rules to get different layouts.

(Dice + map art by @brstf)

PDFs of the original still free at: https://awkwardturtle.itch.io/wallet-dungeons
